{
  "translationLines": [
    {
      "lineNumber": 210022,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「あんなでかいモンスターも倒せるなんて、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Being able to defeat such a huge monster,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 210023,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　もう世界最強級に強いんじゃね？",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "aren't you already among the strongest in the world?"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 210024,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　もうかなりヤバくね？　激ヤバじゃね？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Isn't that seriously crazy? Like insanely strong?"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 210025,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「うんうん、そうだすなぁ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Yeah, yeah, that's right.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 210026,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「おらは昔、ランス様と一緒に世界レベルの",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"A long time ago, I went on adventures with Sir Rance and"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 210027,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　すごい方々と冒険したことがあるだすが、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "some incredible people of world-class level,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 210028,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　＜エール＞様の強さはその方々と遜色ないだ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "but the strength of Lord <Yell> is on par with those people.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 210029,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「だしょー？　だしょー？",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Right? Right?"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 210030,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　やっぱロッキーさんもそう思う？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Rocky, you think so too, right?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 210031,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「…………」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"........\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 210032,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "長田君がニヤリと笑った。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Nagata-kun grinned slyly."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 210033,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ぃよーし、＜エール＞！",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Alright, <Yell>!"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 210034,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　もうこうなったら『魔王の子』達を",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Now that it's come to this, let's make the 'Demon King's Children'"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 210035,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　仲間にするこたーねぇぜ！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "our allies!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 210036,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「へ？　どういうことだすか？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Huh? What do you mean?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 210037,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「＜エール＞ちゃん、既に魔王ランスと",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"<Yell>-chan, I see that you already have the strength"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 210038,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　張り合えるだけの強さがあると俺は見たね",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "to rival the Demon King Rance.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 210039,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「世界の各地にいる魔王の子を",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"If you try to make all the Demon King's Children scattered around the world"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 210040,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　いちいち仲間にしてたら、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "your allies one by one,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 210041,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　何年あっても足りないってゆーかー？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "you'd need years and years—doesn't that make no sense?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 210042,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「サクッと魔王ランスのもとに行けば",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"If you just go straight to the Demon King Rance,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 210043,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　面倒なくていいんじゃね？　みたいな！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "it'll be easier and less troublesome, right? Like that!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 210044,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「だっろー？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Isn't that right?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 210045,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ちんたら冒険なんて",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Dragging out a slow adventure"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 210046,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　俺らの性に合わないって！",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "doesn't suit our style!"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 210047,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　今時は何事もサクッと終わらせるもんだぜー」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "These days, you gotta get things done quickly!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 210048,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「うーん、今の＜エール＞様が勝てるか",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Hmm, whether Lord <Yell> can win right now"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 210049,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　どうかはおらには分からないだすが……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "I don't really know... but...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 210050,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「でも、ランス様も自分の子供に",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"But, I think Sir Rance wouldn't do anything harsh"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 210051,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　ひどいことはしないと思うだすし、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "to his own children,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 210052,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　早い内に行くのはいいかも知れないだすな」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "so maybe it's good to go there sooner rather than later.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 210053,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ほらほらー、ロッキーさんだって",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"See, see? Even Rocky's saying so,\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 210054,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　こう言ってるっしょー？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "right?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 210055,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「…………」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"........\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 210056,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ウケる」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"That's funny.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 210057,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ぷはーっ！",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Puhah!"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 210058,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　＜エール＞ちゃーん、真面目すぎー！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "<Yell>-chaaan, you're way too serious!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 210059,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「今、調子に乗らないで、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"If you don't start getting cocky now,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 210060,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　いつ調子に乗んの？　ってレベルだって！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "then when will you? That's how much you're at that level!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 210061,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「大丈夫、大丈夫！",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"It's okay, it's okay!"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 210062,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　＜エール＞ちゃんが最強なのは、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "I guarantee that <Yell>-chan is the strongest!"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 210063,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　この俺が保証すっから！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 210064,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「うーん、今の＜エール＞様が勝てるか",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Hmm, whether Lord <Yell> can win right now"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 210065,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　どうかはおらには分からないだすが……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "I don't really know... but...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 210066,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「でも、ランス様も自分の子供に",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"But, I think Sir Rance wouldn't do anything harsh"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 210067,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　ひどいことはしないと思うだすし、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "to his own children,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 210068,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　早い内に行くのはいいかも知れないだすな」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "so maybe it's good to go there sooner rather than later.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 210069,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ほらほらー、ロッキーさんだって",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"See, see? Even Rocky's saying so,\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 210070,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　こう言ってるっしょー？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "right?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 210071,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「おいおい、何びびってんだよ！",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Hey, hey, what are you scared of!"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 210072,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　だいじょーぶ！　だいじょーぶ！",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "It's all good! It's all good!"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 210073,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　心配性だなー、＜エール＞はー！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "You're such a worrywart, <Yell>!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 210074,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「あ、でも、おらも大丈夫だって思うだす」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Ah, but I also think it will be fine.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 210075,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「だってランス様が自分の子供に",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Because I can't imagine Sir Rance doing anything"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 210076,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　ひどいことするって思えないだすから、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "cruel to his own children,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 210077,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　きっと戦闘にもならないだすよ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "so surely it won’t even come to a fight.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 210078,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ほらほらー、ロッキーさんだって",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"See, see? Even Rocky's saying so,\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 210079,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　こう言ってるっしょー？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "right?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 210080,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「よーっし！　決定！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Alright! It's decided!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 210081,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「えーと、今、俺達がここにいてー」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Umm, right now we’re here—\""
    }
  ]
}

